C---  IFL =  0 : F2 sucessfully calculated
C---         1 : Fast calculation
C---        -1 : Scale mu outside grid
 
      IMPLICIT DOUBLE PRECISION (A-H,O-Z)
 
 
      COMMON/QCCONS/
